<td><strong>IMPORTANT:Â  </strong>UCI has a new loan servicer, starting with Fall 2017 quarter.Â  You will be notified when and how to login at the servicer&#8217;s web site to complete loan processing online.Â  If you follow the servicer&#8217;s instructions, there will be plenty of time for loans to post to your Zot Account before the September 15, 2017 registration fee payment deadline.</td>
